    "Title": "Silent Strike",
    "Description": "Any interest in taking out a <EM4>~mission(AmbushTarget)</EM4> for us? \n\nShouldn\u2019t be too much trouble. We\u2019ve already done the legwork and figured out that they're scheduled to pass by <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> soon. Just go dark in the nearby emission cloud and you\u2019ll get a good jump on \u2018em.  \n\nThey might roll through solo or with some friends. All would be single-seaters but they can hold their own in a dogfight. We\u2019ll drop some forces in the region who can provide support once the fun starts.\n\nYou pull this off and I'll toss <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) Council Scrip</EM4> to the main contractor for a job well done.\n\n- Stows",
